import React from 'react'
import { Grid, Image, Message } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Landing = () => (
  <Grid celled='internally'>
    <Grid.Row>
      <Grid.Column width={3}>
        <Message> Test </Message>
      </Grid.Column>
      <Grid.Column width={10}>
      <Message> Test </Message>
      </Grid.Column>
      <Grid.Column width={3}>
      <Message> Test </Message>
      </Grid.Column>
    </Grid.Row>

    <Grid.Row>
      <Grid.Column width={3}>
      <Message> Test </Message>
      </Grid.Column>
      <Grid.Column width={10}>
      <Message> Test </Message>
      </Grid.Column>
      <Grid.Column width={3}>
      <Message> Test </Message>
      </Grid.Column>
    </Grid.Row>
  </Grid>
)

export default Landing
